{"tid":797327,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張祺忠：社會雙重標準評價暴力","createTime":"2018-08-28T12:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T14:11:07.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"abea6cd4484c3b7c848e1d2fb35efd7752e6f207","tid":797327,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:12:30.000Z","msg":"2015年8月3日 12:20  Share to Facebook<br />\n【now新聞台】中大前校長劉遵義在報章撰文形容衝擊港大校務委員會是暴徒行為，應該監禁涉事年輕人；港大校務委員張祺忠認為學生是否暴力可以商榷。<br />\n<br />\n港大校務委員劉麥嘉軒丈夫、中大前校長劉遵義在在《明報》撰文，形容上周二衝擊校務委員會是暴徒行為，不應在任何文明社會發生，遑論高等學府，年輕人應對不同觀點保持開放、包容和謙卑，否則不應上大學。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，事件令人質疑納稅人的錢是否應繼續用於這些自我中心、不尊重其他人「被寵壞的小混蛋」身上，認為他們應該得到教訓，例如監禁一日或做100小時社會服務。<br />\n<br />\n劉遵義強調撰文並非因太太麥嘉軒被暴徒追截、咒罵而撰文，亦非就港大任命副校長給予意見。<br />\n<br />\n港大校務委員張祺忠出席本台節目時表示，學生當日語言激烈，但是否暴力可以商榷。<br />\n<br />\n港大校董鍾樹根認為，又指就算部分衝入會議廳或在樓下聲援人士不是學生，背後亦是同一班人計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=145545\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D145545&d=aakwICR1GkIzRDVbDCEzlGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=c022d7c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D145545&h=13372682\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=145545</a>"},{"pid":"fac77953d122560c430883838afe25e54ef477d7","tid":797327,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087aa2cbc89123746f75a4783d1277cdded9e31a","tid":797327,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T13:05:40.000Z","msg":"俾人拉咗<br />\n罪名<del>又係</del>殺妻<br />\n唔知關唔關維護學生事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e3faf4ad9e74f5eaeaf602c3ddc49367a4d400","tid":797327,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T13:38:07.000Z","msg":"個社會已經得返一套標準去評價暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6d8c06df7b47bee8cba90c5da95f9630d9724b","tid":797327,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T14:11:07.000Z","msg":"又係同港獨同佔中有關"}]}